Title: RESTAPI: evaluate accept header
Class: feature
Compatible: incomp
Component: core
Date: 1633434450
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p13

In previous version the accept header of the HTTP-request was completely
ignored.

With this werk the accept header can still be omitted, but if it is set to a
value that can not be satisfied by the REST-API it will return an error with an
406 status code.
